'''Mitsuko Kongō''' (Japanese:{{ruby|婚后|こんごう|ja}}{{ruby|光子|みつこ|ja}}) is a character of the light novel series [[A Certain Magical Index]] and [[A Certain Scientific Railgun]].
She is a second grade transfer student of [[Tokiwadai Middle School]], and a level 4 Aero Hand. Born and raised in a wealthy family, she grown up as a spoiled one with less knowledge with the world. Always do things that she actually could not. She is pride and innocent, but still, a kind person. She has a ratsnake called "Ekaterina-chan."
